---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import app1 from '../../assets/app1.webp';
import app2 from '../../assets/app2.webp';
---

<div class='other-container'>
  <div class='others-wrapper'>
    <p class='other-overtext'>React / Typescript</p>
    <div class='other one'>
      <Image class='other-img' src={app1} alt='landing page' />
    </div>
    <h3 class='other-text'>
      My first application written based on experience from the financial
      industry and drawing on knowledge from client work.
    </h3>
    <h3 class='other-text'>
      Helps to quickly calculate returns on both bank deposits and investment
      funds, without the need for online calculators. Try my app <a
        aria-label='link to app site'
        href='https://letscountit.netlify.app/'>Let's Count It</a>
    </h3>
  </div>

  <div class='others-wrapper'>
    <p class='other-overtext'>Canva / Figma</p>
    <div class='other two'>
      <Image class='other-img' src={app2} alt='happy family sitting' />
    </div>
    <h3 class='other-text'>
      Design and production of an interior design e-book for a major influencer
      in Poland.
    </h3>
    <h3 class='other-text'>
      A big challenge with this project was learning new tools such as Canva and
      Figma. The aforementioned e-books were a great addition to the website I
      created. <a
        aria-label='link to app site'
        href='https://stowidokowhome.pl/'>stowidokow.home</a>
    </h3>
  </div>

  <div class='others-wrapper'>
    <p class='other-overtext'>React / Typescript</p>
    <div class='other one'>
      <Image class='other-img' src={app1} alt='happy family sitting' />
    </div>
    <h3 class='other-text'>
      Cooperation on the website <a
        aria-label='link to spelnij-marzenia site'
        href='https://www.spelnij-marzenia.pl/'>Spe≈Çnij Marzenia</a
      >
    </h3>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .other-container {
    margin-top: 50px;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    display: grid;
    gap: 50px;
    z-index: 10;
    position: relative;
  }
  .others-wrapper {
    border: none;
    border-radius: 15px;
    display: grid;
    padding: 5px;
    grid-template-rows: subgrid;
    grid-row: span 4;
    gap: 0px;
  }
  .other {
    border-radius: 15px;
  }
  .other.one {
    background-color: rgb(191, 205, 235);
  }
  .other.two {
    background-color: rgb(236, 117, 48);
  }
  .other-img {
    object-fit: contain;
    max-width: 100%;
    padding: 15px 0;
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .other-overtext {
    margin-bottom: 5px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-family: var(--second-font);
    color: var(--light-grey);
  }
  .other-text {
    margin-top: 10px;
    font-family: var(--second-font);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  .other-text a {
    color: var(--bg-black);
  }
</style>
